title: How To Lose Weight During the Holidays, Part 1
itunes:title: How To Lose Weight During the Holidays, Part 1
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

Let's get geared up for the holidays!

In the PNPTribe the girls have a whole program called Handling the Holidays Like a Boss Lady and today we give you two of the key tools we use.

We often are worried about the overspending, overeating, overthinking, or over drinking. Basically we are over the holidays before they even happen because we think of all the problems we will face with food pushers and more.

Today we will help you cut through the crap thoughts and get into the spirit of the season.
